label may_2019_library_date:

    stop music
    scene black
    with Pause(1)

    show splash with pixellate
    show text "That weekend..." with dissolve
    play sound yooo
    $ renpy.pause(10, hard=True)

    scene black with pixellate
    with Pause(1)

    play music calc_studying

    scene bg public_library

    show tanish neutral at mid_right
    show cindy sad at mid_left
    show chunky at center

    tanish "Alright. Math time. Let's suffer."

    cindy "Ugh. Do we have to?"

    tanish "If we don’t, we fail and bring shame to Chunky the jade plant."

    show cindy neutral at mid_left

    cindy "Fine. Chunky wouldn’t want that."

    tanish "Start with derivatives?"

    cindy "Yeah... chain rule is still my enemy, thanks to Mr. Retardick... I mean Retallack."

    tanish "Lucky for you, I am slightly less dumb at this now."

    cindy "Flex."

    tanish "Nah seriously, look—let's do this one."

    play sound flipping_page

    tanish "f(x) = (3x² + 1)^4"

    cindy "Oh god."

    tanish "You got this. It’s outer function to the power of 4, right?"

    cindy "So... 4(3x² + 1)^3?"

    tanish "Yep. Now chain rule—the inner derivative?"

    cindy "6x?"

    tanish "Perfect."

    pause

    cindy "So the whole derivative is... 4(3x² + 1)^3 * 6x"

    show tanish happy at mid_right
    tanish "Which is... 24x(3x² + 1)^3. Nailed it."

    cindy "Okay wait, that actually made sense."

    tanish "Told you. You just needed a real tutor and a fictional plant mascot."

    show cindy happy at mid_left
    cindy "Chunky delivers again."

    tanish "Chunky is the MVP of this arc."

    cindy "Next one’s yours."

    tanish "Bring it on."

    play sound flipping_page
    pause

    scene black
    show text "A few hours later..." with dissolve
    with Pause(3)

    scene bg public_library

    show tanish neutral at mid_right
    show cindy neutral at mid_left
    show chunky at center

    tanish "Okay, that was like... 40\% productivity."

    cindy "Better than I expected."

    tanish "You want a break?"

    cindy "Desperately."

    tanish "Cool. Let's wander and touch books like we read for fun."

    cindy "Scandalous."

    hide tanish with moveoutright
    hide cindy with moveoutright

    pause
    scene bg library_shelf

    show tanish happy at left
    show cindy neutral at right

    tanish "Yo. Hold up."

    cindy "What?"

    tanish "This manga is literally called... 'The Erotic Adventures of Kana and Diona.'"

    show cindy happy at right

    cindy "No way."

    tanish "I swear, look."

    cindy "How is this even in the public library?"

    tanish "I don't even know, someone must have donated it or something."

    cindy "Wait—are you actually opening it?"

    show tanish blush at left
    tanish "For academic purposes."

    cindy "Purely educational."

    tanish "Of course. This is... wow. They’re in a hot spring by page five."

    cindy "Classic."

    play sound flipping_page
    pause

    tanish "You know what's weird? The art’s actually good."

    cindy "Unironically yes."

    play sound flipping_page

    tanish "We're gonna accidentally read this whole thing, aren't we?"

    cindy "We already read half. You turned pages."

    play sound flipping_page

    tanish "You told me to keep going."

    cindy "Because I was invested."

    play sound flipping_page
    play sound laugh

    scene black
    stop music
    show text "A while later..." with dissolve
    with Pause(3)

    play music library
    scene bg library_shelf

    show tanish blush at middle_right
    show cindy neutral at middle_left

    tanish "awww you pre cute... can I touch your hair?"

    show cindy blush at middle_left
    cindy "... umm... sure i guess?"

    tanish "okay sweetie"

    pause

    cindy "mmm... that's nice"

    play sound kiss
    pause

    tanish "Holy SHIT, its already night outside!"

    cindy "When did it get dark?"

    tanish "Okay, let’s not get locked in here. Food?"

    cindy "Please. Brain empty."

    hide tanish with moveoutleft
    hide cindy with moveoutleft

    pause

    scene black
    with Pause(1)

    scene bg cafe

    show tanish blush at middle_left
    show cindy blush at mid_right

    tanish "I forgot how nice this place is."

    cindy "Ambiance 10 out of 10. Menu prices? Less so."

    tanish "Worth it though. They’ve got that one sandwich with the pesto... life-changing."

    cindy "I’m getting the mushroom melt. Carbs over stress."

    tanish "Respect."

    tanish "You want anything to drink?"

    cindy "Ginger ale. Always."

    tanish "Classy. I’ll get the iced chai."

    
    show tanish happy at middle_left
    show cindy happy at mid_right
    show sandwich1 at table_center
    show sandwich2 at table_right
    tanish "Okay... this sandwich is exactly how I remembered it. Messy and glorious."

    cindy "This bread is doing emotional healing."

    tanish "Chunky would be proud of our choices."

    cindy "Chunky demands we honor the carb gods."

    play sound eating
    pause

    show cindy blush at mid_right

    tanish "So... aside from plants and drawings, what else do you do?"

    cindy "Honestly? Not much. School kinda drains me. I like netflix though. Maybe some chilling too."

    cindy "What about you? Aside from being weirdly good at chain rule?"

    show tanish happy at middle_left
    tanish "I dabble. Anime, Osu!, occasionally drawing cursed dragons... gaming when I have energy."

    cindy "Do your dragons breathe fire or anxiety?"

    tanish "Mostly self-doubt. Sometimes boba."

    cindy "Incredible. I’d read that webcomic."

    tanish "I’ll write it just for you."

    play sound eating
    pause

    hide sandwich1
    hide sandwich2


    show tanish neutral at middle_left
    show cindy neutral at mid_right

    tanish "You ready to bounce?"

    cindy "Yeah. Let’s head out."

    tanish "Cool, I’ll go pay—"

    show tanish left at middle_left
    tanish "...Wait."

    play sound ohno
    pause

    show cindy blush at mid_right
    cindy "?"

    tanish "...I forgot my wallet."

    tanish "I swear I had it this morning. I must’ve left it on my desk."

    pause

    show cindy happy at mid_right
    cindy "It’s fine. I got it."

    show tanish neutral at middle_left
    tanish "Are you sure? I’ll e-transfer you right now."

    cindy "Seriously. It’s okay. Just cover me next time."

    show tanish happy at middle_left
    tanish "You’re a lifesaver. I owe you fries forever."

    cindy "Noted. Interest accrues daily."

    tanish "Damn. You’re ruthless."

    hide tanish with moveoutright
    hide cindy with moveoutright

    scene black
    with Pause(1)

    scene bg cindy_room

    show cindy neutral at center

    cindy "That was actually fun..."

    cindy "He’s goofy, but sweet."

    cindy "Still... forgetting his wallet?"

    cindy "Also... asking if he could touch my hair...?"

    cindy "I don’t know. Felt a little off and awkward."

    cindy "But I’ll give him the benefit of the doubt."

    return
